Package: NetworkUtils
Type: Package
Title: Provides network subsetting and measure-generating functionality for the DVN. 
Version: 0.1
Date: 2009-05-18
Author: Alexander D'Amour 
Maintainer: <adamour@iq.harvard.edu>
Description: Uses igraph as a backend to support manual vertex and edge queries, component-based subsetting, and measure generation. 
Depends: igraph (>= 0.5), Matrix
License: GPL 
LazyLoad: yes
